text: Chakwal District () is a district in the Punjab province of Pakistan. The city of Chakwal is the capital. ==Administration== The district is administratively subdivided into five tehsils and 68 Union Councils * Chakwal Tehsil * Choa Saidan Shah Tehsil * Talagang Tehsil * Kallar Kahar Tehsil * Lawa Category:Chakwal District Category:Rawalpindi Division
title: Chakwal District
